    "Thus, CNN appears to be more competent in interpreting the Malaysian dataset.",
    "The CNN-LSTM model produced nearly identical R2 scores for both countries, at approximately 0.847.",
    "However, it is worth noting that the MAPE for Malaysia was substantially higher at 4.955, which is almost five times the UAE score.",
    "This suggests that, while the model might fit the data similarly, it is less reliable in terms of percentage error for Malaysia.",
    "Hence, in this rare instance, CNN-LSTM seems to offer slightly better performance for the UAE, despite having an equal R2 score."
